---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="First-Time China Travel Guide"
  description="A practical starting point for first-time China travelers: payments, apps, transport, hotels, and trip planning."
  canonical="/china-travel/"
>
  <section class="content-page">
    <div class="page-header">
      <span class="eyebrow">First-time China travel</span>
      <h1>Plan a smoother first trip to China.</h1>
      <p>
        Focus on the high-friction basics first: mobile payments, internet access, transport, hotel location, and a
        simple daily route plan.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="content-grid">
      <div class="prose">
        <h2>Core topics</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>How to set up Alipay or WeChat Pay as a foreign visitor</li>
          <li>Best China travel apps for maps, translation, trains, and ride hailing</li>
          <li>How to choose hotels near metro lines and trade districts</li>
          <li>High-speed rail basics for first-time visitors</li>
          <li>City guides for Guangzhou, Shanghai, Beijing, Shenzhen, Yiwu, and Hangzhou</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Start with these guides</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>China travel checklist for first-time visitors</li>
          <li>Can foreigners use Alipay in China?</li>
          <li>China eSIM vs local SIM card</li>
          <li>How to take high-speed trains in China</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <aside class="sidebar">
        <div class="notice-box">
          <h2>Starter guide</h2>
          <p>Use the checklist to cover the basics before you book transport, hotels, and daily routes.</p>
          <a class="button secondary" href="/blog/china-travel-checklist-first-time-visitors/">Read checklist</a>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
